    "As for the another important task, i.e., knowledge graph construction, which refers to creating a structured representation of knowledge, LLMs can be applied in the process of constructing knowledge graphs, including entity discovery [71,72], coreference resolution [73,74] and relation extraction [75,76].",
    "LLMs can also achieve the end-to-end construction [57,65,70,77,78] to directly build KGs from raw text.",
    "LLMs enable the knowledge distillation to construct knowledge graphs.",
    "symbolic-kg [79] distills commonsense facts from GPT3 and then finetunes the small student model to generate knowledge graphs.",
    "These models have demonstrated the capacity to store large volumes of knowledge, providing a viable option for improving the scope and depth of knowledge graphs."
